headline: Dow Jones Tech Titan Apple Stock, Alibaba In Or Near Buy Zones Despite Market Sell-Off
summary: Dow Jones tech titan Apple stock and Chinese leader Alibaba are in or near buy zones despite Tuesday's stock market sell-off.
